    Cost-sens total cost : €     -46,609,672
    Reduction            : €       3,073,059  (+7.06% of |baseline|)
    Mean reduction / PTU : €320.85
    Wilcoxon: W=21430094, p=4.511e-06  ← significant
    t-test  : t=8.7544, p=2.399e-18  ← significant
    Cohen's d: 0.0895

  Test (2025) — Single pricing (n=25,458):
